		<title>Chelsea ready to test Hazard resolve</title>
		<link>http://www.onlinesportson.net/chelsea-ready-to-test-hazard-resolve.html</link>
					<comments>http://www.onlinesportson.net/chelsea-ready-to-test-hazard-resolve.html#respond</comments>
		
